      <memberdef kind="function" id="xilflash__cfi_8h_1a025ba2cd783a06301dc7caa4fb537d95" prot="public" static="no" const="no" explicit="no" inline="no" virt="non-virtual">
        <type>int</type>
        <definition>int XFlashCFI_ReadCommon</definition>
        <argsstring>(XFlash *InstancePtr, u8 BusWidth)</argsstring>
        <name>XFlashCFI_ReadCommon</name>
        <param>
          <type>XFlash *</type>
          <declname>InstancePtr</declname>
        </param>
        <param>
          <type>u8</type>
          <declname>BusWidth</declname>
        </param>
        <briefdescription>
<para>Retrieves the standard CFI data from the part(s), interpret the data, and update the provided geometry and properties structures. </para>        </briefdescription>
        <detaileddescription>
<para>Extended CFI data is part specific and ignored here. This data must be read by the specific flash device family library.</para><para><parameterlist kind="param"><parameteritem>
<parameternamelist>
<parametername>InstancePtr</parametername>
</parameternamelist>
<parameterdescription>
<para>is the pointer to the XFlash instance. </para></parameterdescription>
</parameteritem>
<parameteritem>
<parameternamelist>
<parametername>BusWidth</parametername>
</parameternamelist>
<parameterdescription>
<para>is the total width of the flash memory, in bytes.</para></parameterdescription>
</parameteritem>
